abstract: WEISBADEN, Germany, July 20 (AP)--William Blankenship of Columbus, Ga., won the center-fire pistol event at the world shooting championships today and helped the United States take the team title.
headline_main: PISTOL TITLE WON BY BLANKENSHIP; Marksman Helps U.S. Gain Team Crown in Germany
